# The build context is the repo root, but the image build only needs the cargo
# workspace sources (Cargo.toml, Cargo.lock, rust-toolchain.toml, crates/) — the
# embedded assets, Askama templates, and SQL migrations all live under crates/.
# Keep the context lean: the compiled target dir lives in BuildKit cache mounts,
# and the local CAS blob store must never be shipped into the build.
/target
**/target
/cas
.git
.gitignore
.gitattributes
.github
.claude
.env
.env.example
.vs/
docker-compose.yml
flake.nix
flake.lock
dist-workspace.toml
release-please-config.json
.release-please-manifest.json
*.md
